ion\n```\n\n---\n\n## Task 18: Verify Metrics Exposure\n**Verifiable Output:** Prometheus metrics are correctly exposed\n\n- [ ] Verify all JWT metrics are registered:\n  - agentcube_jwt_tokens_generated_total\n  - agentcube_jwt_tokens_validated_total\n  - agentcube_jwt_validations_failed_total\n  - agentcube_jwt_validation_duration_seconds\n  - agentcube_jwt_active_refresh_tokens\n- [ ] Test metrics endpoint returns JWT data:\n  - Generate tokens and verify counter increments\n  - Validate tokens and verify counter increments\n  - Force failures and verify error counters\n- [ ] Verify metric labels are correct\n- [ ] Test metric values after operations\n- [ ] Run with `-tags=integration`\n\n**Verification Command:**\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/router/... -v -run \"TestJWTMetricsExposure\" -tags=integration\n```\n\n---\n\n## Task 19: Verify Compatibility with AR-009\n**Verifiable Output:** JWT integrates with Router HTTP Core\n\n- [ ] Verify JWT middleware works with existing handlers:\n  - Wrap existing handlers with JWT authentication\n  - Verify proxy handler still functions\n  - Verify health check endpoint accessible\n- [ ] Verify no breaking changes to AR-009 interfaces\n- [ ] Verify Server can initialize JWTManager\n- [ ] Test authenticated routes work correctly\n- [ ] Test public routes (health, metrics) remain accessible\n\n**Verification Command:**\n```bash\ngo build ./pkg/router/... && \\\ngo test ./pkg/router/... -v -run \"TestAR009Compatibility\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Task 20: Verify Compatibility with AR-010\n**Verifiable Output:** JWT integrates with Session Management\n\n- [ ] Verify JWT tokens contain session claims:\n  - session_id from SessionInfo\n  - sandbox_id from SessionInfo\n  - namespace from SessionInfo\n- [ ] Verify session validation in JWT middleware:\n  - Active session allows request\n  - Terminated session rejects request\n  - Expired session rejects request\n- [ ] Verify no breaking changes to AR-010 interfaces\n- [ ] Test session-JWT integ